WEBVTT

00:10:58.302 --> 00:11:00.160
to your access to college,

00:11:00.184 --> 00:11:01.912
your access to jobs,

00:11:01.936 --> 00:11:03.644
your access to the future.

00:11:05.594 --> 00:11:10.864
Until we live in a world where every kid
can get a high-quality education

00:11:10.888 --> 00:11:12.424
no matter where they live,

00:11:12.448 --> 00:11:14.328
or the color of their skin,

00:11:14.352 --> 00:11:18.412
there are things we can do
on a macro level.

00:11:19.389 --> 00:11:22.953
School funding should not
be decided by property taxes

00:11:22.977 --> 00:11:25.208
or some funky economic equation

00:11:25.232 --> 00:11:28.268
where rich kids continue
to benefit from state aid,

00:11:28.292 --> 00:11:32.377
while poor kids are continuously
having food and resources